description:
two images mounted on one sheet both from \"Tarfereel Van de Belacchende Werelt\"; 

a) crowd of people in street; richly dressed man in center with medical instrument in hand pointed at eye of pooly dressed man with long beard leaning on a crutch; richly dressed woman seated behind holding/supporting poor man

b) two figures in room with canopied bed; woman seated with feet up at fire; man washing floor; table set for meal in center background; painting of  ships on wall above table
